        "label": "Oyster administrator actor email",
        "setup": "For certain endpoints used with client-credentials authentication, include the email address of a User with an Administrator role in the Oyster account in the `X-Oyster-Actor-Email` header, as documented in [Client credentials authorization](https://docs.oysterhr.com/docs/client-credentials-authorization). This is not minted separately; use an existing Oyster admin user's email address."
